Bloomberg Expects ‘Strong Category 1 Storm’ in New York as Soon as Tonight

-- B y   M a r k   T a n n e n b a u m
-- 
2011-08-27T13:37:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-27/bloomberg-expects-strong-category-1-storm-in-new-york-as-soon-as-tonight.html
New York City Mayor  Michael
Bloomberg  said he expects a “strong Category 1” storm to hit
the region as soon as tonight as Hurricane Irene headed toward
the Northeast after making landfall in  North Carolina .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
